<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>Happy Birthday</title><style>*{box-sizing:border-box}body{margin:0;overflow:hidden;font-family:Arial;background:radial-gradient(circle at top,#4b006e,#120024 45%,#05010d);color:#fff}.bg,.bg:before,.bg:after{position:fixed;inset:-20%;content:"";background:radial-gradient(circle,#ff89c855 2px,transparent 3px) 0 0/60px 60px;animation:spin 80s linear infinite}.bg:after{filter:blur(2px)}@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}.card{position:relative;z-index:2;width:90%;max-width:820px;margin:8vh auto;padding:35px;border-radius:24px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.55);transform:perspective(900px) rotateX(8deg)}h1{text-align:center;font-size:3rem}button{display:block;margin:20px auto;padding:16px 34px;border:none;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(45deg,#ff4d94,#8a2be2);color:#fff;font-size:20px}#msg{display:none}.heart{position:fixed;animation:fall linear forwards}@keyframes fall{from{transform:translateY(-10vh)}to{transform:translateY(110vh)}}</style></head><body><div class="bg"></div><div class="card"><h1>🎂 Happy Birthday Sabnoor ❤️</h1><button onclick="s()">✨ Surprise Kholo ✨</button><div id="msg"><p>Meri Pyari <b>Sabnoor</b>,<br><br>Hamare pyaar ko <b>2 saal</b> ho gaye. Tum meri zindagi ki sabse khoobsurat wajah ho. Allah tumhe hamesha khush rakhe. ❤️<br><br><b>Happy Birthday Meri Jaan.</b><br>Hamesha Tumhara,<br><b>Ahsan ❤️</b></p></div></div><script>function s(){document.getElementById("msg").style.display="block";for(let i=0;i<80;i++){let h=document.createElement("div");h.className="heart";h.innerHTML="💖";h.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";h.style.animationDuration=(4+Math.random()*5)+"s";document.body.appendChild(h);}}</script></body></html>
